{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"436231d495","title":"大字报——人与“人”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"250bf446d2","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":27,"articleId":"436231d495"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"aa121735ba","name":"张生彬"},{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e467b5b9ac","type":"title","text":"大字报——人与“人”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"220a9f162e","type":"authors","text":"南开大学张生彬","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"45a9af5c6b","type":"subtitle","text":"[张生彬：南开大学中文系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"e04a57a04d","type":"appellation","text":"1、流沙河同志仅写了〈草木篇〉就被剥去了通信权，应声虫叫他“离开地球”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"bc7298de1a","type":"appellation","text":"2、中文系在肃反中斗了三个同学，他们何罪之有？不得而知。可是他们带着心灵的创伤去工作，不知是否要带着创伤走进坟墓。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"c65c70ffc3","type":"appellation","text":"3、我们怀着惴惴的心，防备那“整”的命运降临！我们没有自己的语言，像八哥一样重复着“整人阶级的辞句”，我们没有自己的行动，只配做“整人阶级”的影子。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"1996538f3e","type":"appellation","text":"4、我们不仅要吃饱穿暖，更重要的是精神和个性的彻底解放！我们大学生要有自己的文艺刊物，我们要自己选出全国学生会、市区学生会。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"75ed3f01a5","type":"appellation","text":"5、请校党委对肃反中的错误作深刻的检讨，并保证不犯此种类的错误。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"a5859bb4d7","type":"appellation","text":"6、（特大的字）我们要自由，我们反对“金鱼缸”式的民主!","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"},{"id":"fbd8609e24","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年5月29日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495"}],"page":{"id":"0d7b9aec42","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"436231d495","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}